::Shredder::

Shredder nods. "I'll try to report periodically. If I can't find
anything, I'll come back as soon as I'm sure there's no one around."

He walks off toward the exit, makes sure that all his useful devices
were with him, and then exits, flying off toward the old location of
the Predacon base.
